#

Gala Apple Smoothie

5 min
$3.5
210 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairynuts

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-freelow-calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

smoothiehealthybreakfast

Description

A refreshing and nutritious smoothie that combines the sweetness of Gala apples with creamy yogurt and a hint of cinnamon.

Ingredients

  • gala apples: 2, cored and chopped
  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • almond milk: 1 cup
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • ice cubes: 1 cup
  • cinnamon powder: 1/2 teaspoon
